        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[To deploy Docusaurus 2.x on GitHub Page]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to this blog.
本篇文章将会介绍如何将Docusaurus部署到GitHub Page上。</p><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="docusaurus是什么">Docusaurus是什么<a class="hash-link" href="#docusaurus是什么" title="标题的直接链接">​</a></h2><p><a href="https://www.docusaurus.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">docusaurus</a>是基于React框架的静态站点生成器，通俗来讲，可以快速生成一个文档网站，可用于打造自己的博客等。</p><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="安装">安装<a class="hash-link" href="#安装" title="标题的直接链接">​</a></h2><ol><li>由于本质是一组npm包的集合，所以需要提前配置好node.js环境</li><li>选择好你准备的项目路径，在此处运行<code>npx create-docusaurus@latest my-website classic</code>，其中my-website是你项目的名字可以自定义，classic是经典的生成模板</li><li>进入my-website路径，使用VS Code或者其它你使用的编译器打开项目，新建一个终端，输入命令<code>npm run start</code>在本地运行项目查看效果，在命令行使用<code>control+c</code>或者<code>crtrl + c</code>退出</li><li>输入命令<code>npm run build</code>构建项目，生成build目录</li></ol><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="部署">部署<a class="hash-link" href="#部署" title="标题的直接链接">​</a></h2><p>众所周知，写好了网站，自然想让它上线，可以让互联网访问。为此，你可以购买服务器和域名尽情客制化你的网站，当然也可以让你自己的电脑做服务器，但是不推荐这一方法。</p><p>GitHub Page提供免费的部署功能，以下是前置条件和介绍。</p><ul><li>你有一个GitHub账号</li><li>你已经配置好本地的Git，例如账户和秘钥</li><li>你会基本的Git操作</li><li>你的电脑已经配置好yarn环境</li></ul><h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="github仓库">GitHub仓库<a class="hash-link" href="#github仓库" title="标题的直接链接">​</a></h3><ol><li>新建GitHub仓库，名称为<code>username.github.io</code>，username是你的账户名称</li><li>不用自动生成README.md</li><li>仓库设置为公开访问</li><li>根据仓库生成页面的提示，将本地已存在的website， pull到这个仓库，git init那些我就不说了，需要注意的是请在第一次pull之前创建分支gh-pages而不是master，因为Docusaurus在GitHub Page的默认部署分支是这个，特别是.io结尾的</li><li>在仓库的setting中，左侧边栏page页面，设置默认分支为gh-pages</li></ol><h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="本地website">本地website<a class="hash-link" href="#本地website" title="标题的直接链接">​</a></h3><p>找到<code>docusaurus.config.js</code>，进行部署的配置</p><div class="language-js codeBlockContainer_MPoW theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_B9tL"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-js codeBlock__0OG thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_gEuF"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">const</span><span class="token plain"> config </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">{</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#36acaa">title</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'Abbys Of Code'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain">   </span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic">//网站的标题</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#36acaa">tagline</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'一只小菜鸡的成长记录'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain">    </span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic">//网站首页的描述</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#36acaa">url</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'https://github.com/MixZou/mixzou.github.io'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain">    </span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic">//你的仓库网址</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#36acaa">baseUrl</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'/'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic">//必须带'/'结尾</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#36acaa">onBrokenLinks</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'throw'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#36acaa">onBrokenMarkdownLinks</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'warn'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#36acaa">favicon</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'img/favicon.ico'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic">// GitHub pages deployment config.</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic">// If you aren't using GitHub pages, you don't need these.</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#36acaa">organizationName</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'mixzou'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic">// 你的 GitHub 用户名</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#36acaa">projectName</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'mixzou.github.io'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic">// Usually your repo name，也是部署后的访问网址</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token literal-property property" style="color:#36acaa">deploymentBranch</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'gh-pages'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic">//设置默认分支</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup_hRr1"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_W9eQ" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_XEyF" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_i9w9" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><p>在终端输入命令<code>yarn deploy</code>，项目将自动进行build，然后部署到你的远程仓库。</p><p>成功后终端会显示<code>Website is live at "https://mixzou.github.io/".
✨  Done in 56.43s.</code></p><p>一般过一两分钟，网站就会变化啦，记得是<code>https://+reponame</code>，不是GitHub仓库地址唷。</p><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="客制化">客制化<a class="hash-link" href="#客制化" title="标题的直接链接">​</a></h2><p>请阅读(<a href="https://www.docusaurus.io/zh-CN/docs/category/guides" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Docusaurus 指南 | Docusaurus</a>)</p>]]></content>
